data.description: There is so much space to spread out in this amazing home tucked away in Fultondale! You will find this to be a nice quiet subdivision where neighbors decorate for the holidays and everyone is friendly.  The home features a large den with faux fireplace and bonus room downstairs in addition to a two car garage and extra half bath downstairs.  New paint and the cutest sunroom you've ever seen await you upstairs along with the three ample bedrooms.  Recent updates include water heater and breaker box in 2020, remodeled bathrooms in 2020, flooring, rails, hvac and gutters with leaf guards were replaced/installed in 2022, and the outside meter box and deck were replaced in 2023.  Come on out to see it today or follow the link to experience the fully interactive 3D tour!!
